source: TEXT_BANKJN601_02997_TODO_00<tab>Obtain slick debris from giant clams.
target: TEXT_BANKJN601_02997_TODO_00<tab>Obtain slick debris from giant clams.

source: TEXT_BANKJN601_02997_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the slick debris to Zukin.
target: TEXT_BANKJN601_02997_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the slick debris to Zukin.

source: TEXT_BANKJN601_02997_ZUKIN_000_000<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, you are familiar with giant clams, yes? They have an appetite to match their prodigious size, and are known to indiscriminately devour random objects that drift by.
target: TEXT_BANKJN601_02997_ZUKIN_000_000<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, you are familiar with giant clams, yes? They have an appetite to match their prodigious size, and are known to indiscriminately devour random objects that drift by.

source: TEXT_BANKJN601_02997_ZUKIN_000_001<tab>I would be grateful if you could seek out these clams, prise them open, and bring back the slick debris you find inside. Four such pieces should suffice.
target: TEXT_BANKJN601_02997_ZUKIN_000_001<tab>I would be grateful if you could seek out these clams, prise them open, and bring back the slick debris you find inside. Four such pieces should suffice.

source: TEXT_BANKJN601_02997_ZUKIN_000_020<tab>Ah, there you are, and with your arms intact. Just as well─we may still have need of them. But come, let us see what the clams have rendered up.
target: TEXT_BANKJN601_02997_ZUKIN_000_020<tab>Ah, there you are, and with your arms intact. Just as well─we may still have need of them. But come, let us see what the clams have rendered up.

source: TEXT_BANKJN601_02997_ZUKIN_000_021<tab>Yes, these are precisely what I sought! You have done well, my friend.
target: TEXT_BANKJN601_02997_ZUKIN_000_021<tab>Yes, these are precisely what I sought! You have done well, my friend.

source: TEXT_BANKJN601_02997_ZUKIN_000_022<tab>When a foreign object settles inside a shell, it gradually develops a hard and lustrous coating. While such articles are not as valuable as a well-formed pearl, they are not without worth. Nor is it unheard of for clams to be holding treasures!
target: TEXT_BANKJN601_02997_ZUKIN_000_022<tab>When a foreign object settles inside a shell, it gradually develops a hard and lustrous coating. While such articles are not as valuable as a well-formed pearl, they are not without worth. Nor is it unheard of for clams to be holding treasures!
